<ul>
<li>Good idea. ArbCom is inadequate at removing problematic administrators. It&#39;s up to the community to remove admins, since they elected them. <b><a href="" title="User:Majorly">&#60;span style=&#34;font-family:verdana; font-size:10pt; color:#6B8AB8&#34;&#62;Majorly&#60;/span&#62;</a></b> <a href="#T" title="User talk:Majorly">&#60;span style=&#34;font-family:verdana; font-size:8pt; color:#6B8AB8&#34;&#62;talk&#60;/span&#62;</a> 21:07, 7 March 2009 (UTC)</li></ul>
