<dl>
<dd>I think if an admin needs 3 months of supervised training to do a decent job, they probably shouldn&#39;t be an admin. I mean, this isn&#39;t rocket science. &#60;font face=&#34;Broadway&#34;&#62;<a href="" title="User:Mr.Z-man">Mr.</a><a href="" title="User talk:Mr.Z-man"><b><i>Z-</i></b><i>man</i></a>&#60;/font&#62; 01:19, 17 March 2009 (UTC)</dd></dl>
<p>S/he doesn&#39;t necessarily need 3 months of supervised training; it&#39;s just a way for us to get more qualified editors out there cleaning up the mess. Please try and look at the spirit of what I&#39;m trying to portray, not just the letter.--<a href="" title="User:Sallicio"><b>It&#39;s me...Sallicio!</b></a><a href="" title="User talk:Sallicio">&#60;sup&#62;&#60;math&#62;\color{Red} \oplus&#60;/math&#62;&#60;/sup&#62;</a> 03:52, 17 March 2009 (UTC)
